<div style="width: 740px; border: 1px dashed gray; padding: 10px;  margin:0px auto;">
<h2>Patient Diet Change</h2><hr />
<span class="title">Screen Overview </span><br />
This screen will capture patient diet changes details, user can change the patient diet type.
<br /><hr /><br />
<img src="images/Diet_patientdietchange.jpg" width="725"  /><br /><br />
<hr />
<p>

<span class="title">Patient diet change (menu click): </span><br />
User can click the patient diet change option from diet menu. Based on login ward all admitted patient list will display
<br />
<span class="title">GRID (Display): </span> <br />
Based on login ward all admitted patient list will display in the form of table. 
<br />
<br />
<span class="title">GRID (Changes): </span> 
<br />
<br />
    <span class="title">Diet Name:</span> 
    <br />User can select the diet name from the given list, this will come from diet screen and it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Therapeutic Diet:</span> 
    <br />User can select the therapeutic diet from the given list, it can remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Diet type:</span> 
    <br />User can select the diet type from the given list, this will come from diet type screen and it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Waking/bed patient: </span> 
    <br />User can select the waking or bed patient from the given list, it can't remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Update (Button): </span> 
    <br />By clicking on update button user can save the data and patient diet will update.
        
</p>
</div>
